query:
SELECT id, county, address, saleDate, saleStatus, currentBid, upsetBidCloseDate
FROM properties 
WHERE saleStatus = 'in_upset_period'
  AND (saleDate IS NULL OR saleDate > NOW())
LIMIT 10;
